title: Did AOC Call GOP ‘Sad’ and ‘Stupid’ for Criticizing Her Outfits?
subtitle: Republicans criticized the expensive price tags on outfits worn by U.S. Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez in a Vanity Fair photo shoot.
author: Nur Ibrahim
vclaim: U.S. Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez called Republicans “sad” and “stupid” after conservatives criticized her for wearing expensive outfits costing $14,000 for a December 2020 Vanity Fair story.
